short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Blue Wizzard's Unofficial Shell Shockers Theme.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is the Unofficial Shell Shockers Theme for BlueWizzardDigital. Made by AtHomeGaming!
This theme changes the look of the game Shell Shockers. It adds the look from Twitch Streamer Blue Wizard Digital.

The colors are easier on the eyes and act as a custom look for Shell Shockers. It is a great Shell Shockers theme, featuring a homepage background, a sound when you kill someone, and MUCH, MUCH MORE!
